1
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,040
Open the main road twelve feet wide

2
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,560
Open the side path eight feet wide

3
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:47,360
Let the soul depart

4
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,320
Let the funeral proceed

5
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:50,880
Commence the procession

6
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,800
Mother, this is your last day

7
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:56,360
Your filial son has kept vigil for you

8
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:58,120
Mother! Mother!

9
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,240
Encoffin

10
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:05,520
The coffin... there's someone inside!

11
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,240
Have you found which shop this coffin came from?

12
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:20,200
I have.

13
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,800
The shop is in Anye Fang.

14
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,040
The shopkeeper said

15
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,240
he checked it just before closing last night.

16
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:27,200
The coffin was hauled away directly this morning.

17
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,440
He didn't expect something like this to happen.

18
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:30,640
Prepare

19
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:31,200
for the autopsy.

20
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,040
Blood spatter patterns.

21
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,000
Consistent with Xiao Lian's manner of death.

22
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,560
Both were nailed to death with coffin nails.

23
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,640
No signs of poisoning.

24
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,080
No obvious fatal external wounds.

25
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,080
Only on the back of the head,

26
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:01,960
there is a bruise.

27
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,280
That means

28
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:08,440
the killer first struck the back of the head with a heavy object

29
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,480
to knock him unconscious.

30
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,720
This also made the wound harder to detect.

31
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,000
Then he was placed inside the coffin,

32
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,280
his hands and feet nailed down.

33
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:29,800
Finally,

34
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,840
a coffin nail was driven into his throat to kill him.

35
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,040
Judging by his pupils,

36
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,120
the time of death

37
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,920
must be over sixty hours ago.

38
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,200
Sixty hours?

39
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,480
That means

40
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,160
Wu Tu'an died before Xiao Lian.

41
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:03,280
Precisely.

42
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,400
The urgent matter now

43
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,320
is to determine the killer's motive.

44
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,320
Is it for money?

45
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:07,920
Is it for passion?

46
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,040
Or is it for revenge?

47
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,200
Guiyi.

48
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:10,800
Yes?

49
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,960
Bring Wang San and An Fu, the coffin bearers from that day,

50
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:13,520
for questioning.

51
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:14,400
Yes, sir.

52
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,160
Hey, Old Yao.

53
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:15,800
Hmm?

54
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:16,600
Can I

55
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,360
ask a favor of Miss Mu?

56
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:22,120
Haven't you troubled her enough already?

57
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,000
Such fake politeness.

58
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,480
I see that you and the Vice Minister

59
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,800
just won't yield to each other,

60
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,840
and neither gives way to the other.

61
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:35,520
Is that so?

62
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:36,800
You...

63
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:37,880
just stay like that for now.

64
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:38,880
And then?

65
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:44,600
Wang San.

66
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,320
Did Wu Tu'an have any grudges against you?

67
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,560
None at all, my lord.

68
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,360
The money you earn from your work,

69
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,160
how is it distributed?

70
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,160
Whoever finds the employer

71
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,720
gets a bigger share.

72
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,000
It has always been this way.

73
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,200
It's fair enough.

74
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,000
We... we all accept it.

75
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,840
How was your relationship

76
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:04,920
with Wu Tu'an and his wife?

77
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,400
Not exactly good,

78
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,880
but not bad either.

79
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:08,880
Aside from work,

80
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:11,040
we didn't interact much.

81
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:12,960
And you?

82
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,840
I didn't know him.

83
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,240
I was just called in to help this time.

84
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,000
Called by whom?

85
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,240
Brother Dongqiu.

86
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,160
My lord,

87
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:31,800
I remember now.

88
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,960
Originally, Wu Tu'an called me,

89
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,520
Brother Dongqiu, and Zhu Zi.

90
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:36,680
We thought

91
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,960
the four of us would bring four apprentices

92
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,160
to get the job done.

93
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,320
But...

94
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,200
Wake up, everyone. Stop sleeping.

95
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:53,840
Wake up.

96
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,040
Mmh.

97
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,280
What's wrong, Brother Dongqiu?

98
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,280
Zhu Zi is so unreliable.

99
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,280
It's almost time to commence the procession, and he's gone.

100
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:03,640
San.

101
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:04,360
You.

102
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:04,840
Go quickly.

103
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,480
Find someone steady to take his place.

104
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:07,520
Right.

105
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,960
An Fu. An Fu will do.

106
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:09,560
Go get him.

107
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,160
Okay.

108
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:10,720
I'm going right now.

109
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,200
Who is Zhu Zi?

110
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,080
A helper at the coffin shop in Anye Fang.

111
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,640
Anye Fang.

112
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,560
Where is he now?

113
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,680
We couldn't find him that night.

114
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,560
And haven't seen him since.

115
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:24,760
Guards!

116
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,000
Go to Anye Fang.

117
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,040
Find this Zhu Zi for me.

118
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:31,760
Yes, sir.

119
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:36,760
Acting Vice Minister.

120
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,200
County Magistrate Zhao of Chang'an County requests an audience.

121
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:38,640
Let him in.

122
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:39,520
Yes, sir.

123
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,080
Acting Vice Minister, you are busy with official duties.

124
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,680
So I will speak right here.

125
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,040
The Evil spirit case that caused such a stir recently...

126
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,280
...is related to the Sun family in Changle Fang.

127
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:52,400
The one being buried that day was the young lady of the Sun family.

128
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,240
Sun Miaoling.

129
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,360
A few days ago, the Chang'an County Magistrate's office...

130
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,240
...received a report.

131
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,240
It stated that someone had gone missing.

132
00:05:59,480 --> 00:05:59,760
Who?

133
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:00,880
The Sun family's son-in-law.

134
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:01,880
Miaoling's husband.

135
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:02,400
Zhao Di.

136
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,080
The Magistrate's office searched for many days.

137
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,400
But there has been no news of him.

138
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,080
I feared delaying the investigation...

139
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,600
...so I reported it as soon as I heard.

140
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:09,960
I see.

141
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,360
My Lord.

142
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,080
Yes?

143
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,120
When did Zhao Di go missing?

144
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,720
On the night of my daughter Miaoling's burial.

145
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,760
He disappeared.

146
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:31,720
Whose room is this?

147
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,680
It is my daughter...

148
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:35,920
...Miaoling's room.

149
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:37,960
Did Zhao Di...

150
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,480
...live in this room?

151
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,480
No.

152
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,360
Miaoling was frail.

153
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,280
To let her sleep peacefully...

154
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,240
...my son-in-law...

155
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,440
...always slept in the wing room.

156
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:50,880
Take a look.

157
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,040
Please.

158
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:11,440
Did your daughter...

159
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,160
...enjoy using incense?

160
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:14,960
Indeed.

161
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,960
My daughter loved fragrances.

162
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,000
My son-in-law...

163
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,640
...often sent people to procure them.

164
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,920
Incense burned all day long.

165
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,360
What kind of person is Zhao Di?

166
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,480
To be honest, My Lord...

167
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,800
...since my son-in-law married into our family...

168
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,120
...he hasn't shown great capability.

169
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,760
But towards my daughter...

170
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,240
...he was extremely devoted.

171
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,640
Take these fragrances, for example.

172
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,720
He went to great lengths to have them found.

173
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,680
I am old and frail.

174
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,280
My days are numbered.

175
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,160
Seeing his sincerity towards my daughter...

176
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:46,920
...I had intended...

177
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,120
...to hand over the family business...

178
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,160
...to the two of them to manage.

179
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:52,720
But who could have known...

180
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,480
...my daughter would pass away first.

181
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:55,880
And immediately after...

182
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:58,080
...my son-in-law also vanished without a trace.

183
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:03,640
Old Yao.

184
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,240
Judging by your expression...

185
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,000
...you seem to have discovered something.

186
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,120
I can't hide anything from you.

187
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,520
To solve this Evil spirit case...

188
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,840
...I'm afraid we must start investigating the Sun family.

189
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:19,480
Old Yao.

190
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,080
Open the coffin to solve the case.

191
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:26,920
Yes.

192
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,440
Open the coffin!

193
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,640
There really is a paper effigy.

194
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,480
Why is this?

195
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,520
Where is my daughter?

196
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,080
Why is this happening?

197
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:04,440
My daughter!

198
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,080
On the day the coffin was carried,

199
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,400
did the coffin move strangely?

200
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:11,840
It did.

201
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,320
That day, before lifting the coffin,

202
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:15,400
the coffin shook inexplicably.

203
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,520
Inside that coffin,

204
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,240
there really was an evil spirit.
